parsedComplaintsResult.impact: The failure of the transmission can cause the vehicle to stall, lose power, or become difficult to control, which can lead to accidents or leave the driver stranded.
symptoms: The transmission slips or hesitates
the check engine light is illuminated
the vehicle stalls or loses power
the transmission makes loud noises or grinding sounds
the vehicle is unable to shift gears.
